SQL Server 2000/2005</span><span style="color: black;">或以上版本（推荐MSSQL2005版本）</span></span></div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="height: 19.65pt;">\r\n				<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-right-color: white; border-bottom-color: white; border-left-color: rgb(79, 129, 189); background-color: rgb(184, 204, 228); font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px; width: 72.65pt; height: 19.65pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" valign="top" width="97">\r\n					<div align="center" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 18px;">\r\n						<span id="ctl00_CphContent_LblTitle"><span style="color: black;">权限要求</span></span></div>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-right-color: rgb(79, 129, 189); border-bottom-color: white; background-color: rgb(237, 242, 248); font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px; width: 338.45pt; height: 19.65pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" valign="top" width="451">\r\n					<div align="left" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n						<span id="ctl00_CphContent_LblTitle"><span style="color: black;">对SQL Server 数据库具有建表、备份的权限</span></span></div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="height: 19.65pt;">\r\n				<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-right-color: white; border-bottom-color: white; border-left-color: rgb(79, 129, 189); background-color: rgb(184, 204, 228); font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px; width: 72.65pt; height: 19.65pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" valign="top" width="97">\r\n					<div align="center" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 18px;">\r\n						<span id="ctl00_CphContent_