</span></div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="height: 19pt;">\r\n				<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-right-color: white; border-bottom-color: rgb(79, 129, 189); border-left-color: rgb(79, 129, 189); background-color: rgb(184, 204, 228); font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px; width: 72.65pt; height: 19pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" valign="top" width="97">\r\n					<div align="center" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 18px;">\r\n						<span id="ctl00_CphContent_LblTitle"><span style="color: black;">带宽要求</span></span></div>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; margin: 0px; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-right-color: rgb(79, 129, 189); border-bottom-color: rgb(79, 129, 189); background-color: rgb(167, 191, 222); font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px; width: 338.45pt; height: 19pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" valign="top" width="451">\r\n					<div align="left" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n						<span id="ctl00_CphContent_LblTitle"><span style="color: black;">10M</span><span style="color: black;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: black;">共享或更高</span></span></div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; white-space: normal;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>　　九、系统安全性</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	安全性是保证政府网站权威及政府形象的关键因素，也是用户十分关注的问题。基于多年的政府网站运营实践与面向动易软件数十万用户的安全管理经验，动易&reg;&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12px;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Calibri">SmartGov</font><span style="font-family: 宋体;">&trade;&nbsp;</span></font></span>系统采用了包含输入验证、密码多层加密、访问限制、疑似木马程序检测工具等在内的多达三十余种的安全防范措施，并建立了动易软件安全紧急处理机制和预警机制。同时，动易&reg;&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12px;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Calibri">SmartGov</font><span style="font-family: 宋体;">&trade;</span></font>&nbsp;</span>系统还特别针对OWASP组织发布的2008年Web应用程序脆弱性10大统计排名，对跨站脚本、注入漏洞、跨站请求伪造、信息泄露等新型主流攻击方式制定了特别的防御方案，并且借助微软Asp.Net的安全特性和功能对各种攻击方式进行全方位的防范，进一步提升了动易&reg;&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Calibri">SmartGov</font><span style="font-family: 宋体;">&trade;&nbsp;</span></font></span></span>系统的安全性能。以下是动易系统安全防范措施举例：</p>\r\n<ul style="padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; zoom: 1; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;">\r\n	<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; zoom: 1;">\r\n		密码保护</li>\r\n	<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; zoom: 1;">\r\n		输入验证</li>\r\n	<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; zoom: 1;">\r\n		访问限制</li>\r\n	<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; zoom: 1;">\r\n		注入漏洞攻击防范</li>\r\n	<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; zoom: 1;">\r\n		跨站脚本攻击防范</li>\r\n	<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; zoom: 1;">\r\n		跨站请求伪造防范</li>\r\n	<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; zoom: 1;">\r\n		信息泄露防范</li>\r\n	<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; zoom: 1;">\r\n		上传下载防范</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; white-space: normal;">\r\n	&hellip;&hellip;等等。<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>　　十、成功案例</strong></p>\r\n<div align="center" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;">\r\n	<font color="#0000ff">案例一：淮安市税务总局（http://www.hags.gov.cn/）</font></div>\r\n<p style="padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; white-space: normal;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align="center" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;">\r\n	<img alt="" class="imgStyle" height="322" src="http://powereasy.net/UploadFiles/jpg/200810/200810150942365960.jpg" width="551" /></div>\r\n<p style="padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; white-space: normal;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align="center" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;">\r\n	<font color="#0000ff">案例二：深圳出入境检验检疫局（http://www.smdtgs.gov.cn/）</font></div>\r\n<p style="padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; white-space: normal;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align="center" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;">\r\n	<img alt="" class="imgStyle" height="354" src="http://powereasy.net/UploadFiles/bmp/200810/200810171451132786.bmp" width="551" /></div>\r\n<p style="padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; white-space: normal;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align="center" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;">\r\n	<div align="center" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n		<font color="#ff0000">更多市局级政府案例请参考：http://www.powereasy.net/Cases/government/</font><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<div align="left" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">\r\n			<br />\r\n			<strong>　　</strong>如果您对 &ldquo;&nbsp; 动易市局级政府网站（电子政务一体化）解决方案 &rdquo; 感兴趣，请通过<a href="http://powereasy.net/PowerEasy/Contact.html" style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204); text-decoration: underline; outline: none; display: inline-block; padding: 0px 3px;"><font color="#ff0000"><u>点击这里</u></font></a>向我们的销售人员进行详细咨询。<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<strong>　　</strong>注意：动易保留在不事先通知的情况下更改定义及其它产品信息的权利，及对促销活动的最终解释权。</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '1');
